Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln the beginning, there was darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随着轰的一声\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.84,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诞生了无限膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless expanding existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间 空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space, and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在所见超乎我们的想象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.93,0:00:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越了客观认知极限\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}beyond the limits of our existence...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.85,0:00:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙"\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in a place we call "The Universe."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它刚柔并济\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is both mighty and meek.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.40,0:00:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的追求 既要利用其影响 又要摆脱其束缚\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Humanity's quest is to harness its power and escape its bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇塞\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Holy cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是宇航员的感受\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is what an astronaut feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它缔造并破坏恒星 行星 星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt creates and breaks the stars, the planets, the galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制着它们的宇宙过山车驾乘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and directs their cosmic roller coaster ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:54.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万有引力是亦友亦敌\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gravity is ourfriend and ourfoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了它我们熟知的生命的将不复存在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Without it, life as we know it would end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.34,0:01:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球将人间蒸发\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Earth would literally explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伟大而神秘之力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is the magnificent and mystifying force...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,支配着宇宙 万有引力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that rules the universe: Gravity.
