Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.00,0:01:25.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,[历史频道] 第二季 第十七集 重力\N[History Channel] The UniverseⅡ 17of19 Gravity
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万有引力是宇宙间最普遍的力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gravity is the most pervasive force in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.46,0:01:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其作用事无巨细 无一例外\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is at work on massive and minute scales...on the routine and the extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冲浪者靠它乘风破浪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A surfer needs it to hang ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你驾驭浪潮 会乘势而下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When you ride a wave, you're going to slide down the front...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会利用重力往前驰骋\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and you're going to use that pull of gravity to get you going.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它使你加速\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's your acceleration force.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.23,0:01:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是你的加速器 重力是你的加速器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's your accelerator. Gravity is your accelerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑雪者利用它纵身滑下山坡\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A skier uses it to race downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑雪者必须依靠它来腾空跃起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A snowboarder must have it to get big air.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它作用于具有质量的一切东西\N包括我们 无时无刻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt acts on everything with mass, including us, 24/7...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是睡着还是站着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even when sleeping or standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球的万有引力 当然啦 总是将我们\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gravity here on Earth, of course, is always accelerating us down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.51,0:02:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉向地球的中心 加速度为每秒每秒32英尺\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}toward the center of the Earth at 32 feet per second squared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在游乐园里 万有引力翻江倒海\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}At a theme park, gravity is the galactic gas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.02,0:02:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让过山车咆哮 人们狂叫\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that makes roller coasters roar and people scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球引力把我们拉下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The gravity of the Earth pulls us down...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们跑得飞快\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and that's going to make us go really, really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有具有质量或能量的物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}All objects with mass or energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.71,0:02:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粒子 人们 行星 恒星 星系\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}particles, people, planets, stars, and galaxies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会产生引力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}produce gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所不能 无处不在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Omnipotent and omnipresent...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万有引力吸引着 管控着 弯曲着 塑造着 制造着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}gravity attracts, governs, warps, shapes, makes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.47,0:03:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攫取着宇宙间所有的物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and takes all matter and mass in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它无处不在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it's pervasive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它远距离影响着一切物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt acts on all things through extremely large distances...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:18.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无一幸免\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and nothing escapes its pull.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是万有引力将我们的太阳系维系在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is gravity that holds our solar system together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引力就是将我们紧抓在地球上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The force of gravity...is basically that thing that holds us on the planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让飞离的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}keeps us from flying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是宇宙胶合剂 将宇宙间的所有物质结合在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt is the cosmic glue that binds all matter in the universe together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想过没有 拿两颗骰子\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lfyou were to imagine taking two dice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:47.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其完全静止在太空中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and putting them perfectly at rest out in the middle of space...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两者保持一公分的距离\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and separating them by a centimeter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来你会看到 经过一小时左右\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}then what you'd see is that over a course of an hour or so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两颗骰子会慢慢地靠拢在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}those two dice would slowly come together and touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万有引力缔造了我们的世界\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gravity made ourworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的太阳形成于引力收缩的气体云\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our Sun formed from a vast cloud of gas...that gravitationally contracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.04,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样 我们的地球也形成于粒子之间的引力作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Similarly, our Earth formed through the gravitational attraction...of little particles, little bitty things...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小不点逐步成长为越来越大的物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}gradually growing into a bigger and bigger object.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到万有引力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When it comes to gravity's pulling power...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,质量与距离是必须要提的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}mass and distance matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它取决于物体的质量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt depends on the masses of each object...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即物体中的物质总量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the amount of matter within each object.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.89,0:04:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它与两个质量的乘积成正比\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So it's proportional to the product of the two masses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 它越大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln otherwords, the bigger it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:40.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对其它物体施加的拉力就越强\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the harder it pulls on other objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还不止这样\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它与物体之间距离的平方成反比\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And it's inversely proportional...to the square of the distance between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 如果你将两个物体之间的距离加倍\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This means ifyou double the distance between two objects...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其引力或拉力就只有原来强度的四分之一了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the attraction or pull is only a quarter of its original strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万有引力的拉力会控制所有物质的运动或移动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The pulling power of gravity lets it direct the motion and movement...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管其在宇宙中有多大\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of all matter, however massive, in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你会看到所有的星系 比如\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So you have whole galaxies, for example...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互围绕着\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}in orbit around each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:18.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星系团都围绕着它们共同的重心运转\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Clusters of galaxies all orbit around their common center of mass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 利用这个无情的力量的实际潜能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But it is the practical potential of harnessing this relentless force...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数百年来一直困扰着科学家\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that has obsessed scientists for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正开始于伽利略 17世纪的真理追求者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt would literally fall to Galileo Galilei, the 17th-century truth-seeker...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首次认识到了引力的存在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to first recognize that gravity even existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽利略发现不同重量的物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Galileo found that objects having a different weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下降的速度相等\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}fall at the same rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有个很重的钢球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So here's a very heavy steel ball...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个同样大小的乒乓球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and a light ping-pong ball of the same size.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我同时将它们落下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And if l drop them at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:02.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们会在同一时间着地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they hit the ground at exactly the same time as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为它们下降的速度相同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}because they fall at the same rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了解释伽利略最深刻的万有引力发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}To illustrate Galileo's most profound gravitational discovery...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即所有物体 无论其质量如何 下降速度相同\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that all objects, regardless of mass, fall at the same rate...
