Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:44.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管其质量如何 以同样的速度将它们拉回地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}indifferent to their mass, back down to Earth at the same rate.
