Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也以完全一样的速度落下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but l'm falling at exactly the same rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不在乎物体有多重\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt doesn't matter how massive something is.
