Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛顿利用数学揭开了一个宇宙之谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Newton used math to unlock a cosmic mystery.
