Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离不长就落下了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and it falls down a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.25,0:10:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给它更多一点速度 它就更远一些\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You give it more speed, it goes a little farther out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就只管增加你想要的力量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now say you could just increase the force all you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它可以跑出50英里 100英里后才落下\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt can go fifty miles, it can go a hundred miles before it fell.
