Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以让炮弹跑得更快更远\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a cannonball can be made to go faster and farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 重力终将胜出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lnevitably, however, gravity wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.15,0:11:03.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将炮弹拉回地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}pulling the cannonball back down to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.07,0:11:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球是圆的 不是平的 所以牛顿意识到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Earth is round and not flat, so Newton realized...
