Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他意识到 必定到了一个速度\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and he realized that there must be a speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.31,0:11:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它就会一路围绕地球\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}where it goes completely around the Earth...
