Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瞧 看到了一个轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and lo and behold, you have an orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过为何月球没有掉向地球呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But why doesn't the Moon fall to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:54.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月球也有一些横向运动\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Moon also has some sideways motion...
