Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些运动加在一起就是围绕地球的轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and the sum of all those motions is an orbit around the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛顿同样意识到地球也是围绕太阳的大自由落体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Newton also realized that the Earth is in a giant freefall around the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于引力打造了轨道 我们地球围绕着太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}With gravity forging the path, our planet rounds the Sun...
