Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:29.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物理学家现在依然沿用他的思想来解决各种问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and physicists are still using his ideas to solve all sorts of problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一些出奇的怪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some ofthem stranger than others...
