Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿到另一头 会是个怎样的情形？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from one side of the planet to the other?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.72,0:12:46.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个疯狂的计划中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln this wild scheme...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将要驱车穿越地球的直线隧道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you would have to drive a straight-line tunnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就利用重力来推动旅客\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}right through the Earth and use gravity alone to propel a traveler...
