Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过事实上 你刚好到达地表\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but, in fact, you reach the surface ofthe Earth exactly.
