Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重力都会用上精确的42分钟将你带到那里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it takes gravity exactly forty-two minutes to get you there.
