Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛顿搞明白了重力的作用\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Newton figured out what gravity does...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而却让才华横溢的爱因斯坦\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it took the brilliance of physicistAlbert Einstein...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来解决它为何会如此的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to work out why it was doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱因斯坦意识到恒星 行星之类的大物体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Einstein realized that gravity is really caused by huge objects...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所产生的引力 其实是在弯曲空间本身\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}like stars and planets, literally bending space itself.
