Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时已经认识到了恒星及行星在可见的宇宙间的轨道\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}realized that orbits of stars and planets in the observable cosmos...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其表现就像牛顿计算所预测的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}behavejust as Newton's math predicted...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了一个:水星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}except one: Mercury.
