Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水星并不是运行在平平的空间 而是弯曲了太阳周围的空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mercury isn't moving in flat space, but curved space around the Sun.
