Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱因斯坦不仅确定了质量弯曲了空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Einstein not only determined that mass warps space...
