Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.95,0:42:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是捕捉到宇宙迄今所发生的最大事件\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is to catch the most massive event that ever occurred in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.25,0:42:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爆炸\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the Big Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.42,0:42:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引力波可能是最好的机会 让我们一睹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gravitywaves may be our best chance to look...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.00,0:42:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧接着宇宙诞生的那一刻\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}very, very close to the beginning of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.84,0:42:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大爆炸30万年后\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}About 300,000 years after the Big Bang...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.72,0:42:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙异常稠密 乃至混沌一片\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the universe was so dense, it was actually opaque to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.81,0:42:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光都难以通过\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Light could not travel through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.93,0:42:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要是光都难以穿透宇宙 什么能穿透呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So if light can't travel through the universe, what can?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.81,0:42:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引力波\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A gravity wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.44,0:42:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是引力波发出的微乎其微的信号\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The problem is a miniscule signal from a gravitywave...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.82,0:42:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚未被捕捉到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}has yet to be caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.11,0:43:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然很困难\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's clearly hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.61,0:43:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 爱因斯坦预言它们时\N自以为是个不错的主意\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ln fact, when Einstein predicted them, he thought it was a nice idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.91,0:43:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而无人能够发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but no one would ever be able to detect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.25,0:43:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有技术的进步才能给我们机会\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's only the advances of technology that give us a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.00,0:43:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LlGO的科学家 宛如星际冲浪者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}LlGO scientists, like astrosurfers...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.26,0:43:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活出精彩 乘风踏浪\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}live for the day when they can hang ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.76,0:43:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对引力波 迎头而上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and ride theirvery own perfect wave of gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.64,0:43:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们看到了 我们认为是引力波的影响\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We've seen what we think are the effects of gravity waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.31,0:43:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是引力波经过的系统里的能量的损失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the loss of energy from a system by way of gravity waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.85,0:43:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们还没有直接发现到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but we never directly detected one.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.69,0:43:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是最后的前沿阵地之一\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's one of the last frontiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.86,0:43:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LIGO科学家的探索一旦成功\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf the LlGO scientists' quest is successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.53,0:43:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到一个引力波的话 那将会改变科学\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they catch a wave, it could change science.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.95,0:43:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我认为长远来看 首先是了解引力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So, l think that long term, it's first to understand gravity...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.62,0:43:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其次 更有意思的是了解宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then, even more interestingly, to understand the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.17,0:43:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万有引力的领地覆盖我们整个宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The force of gravity has domain over our universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.00,0:44:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它创造并能够毁灭宇宙 恒星 行星 以及人类\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt created and can destroy the cosmos, the stars...the planets, and the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.51,0:44:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它主宰着我们的生活 我们的玩耍 我们的努力\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt controls our lives, our play, and our endeavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.06,0:44:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是宇宙芭蕾\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And therein is this cosmic ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.32,0:44:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们共同的未来取决于宇宙强大的统治者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Our collective future depends on the grace and greatness...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.74,0:44:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万有引力的恩泽与博爱\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of the mighty ruler of the cosmos, gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.00,0:44:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks For Viewing
